text: Sympleurotis armatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Gahan in 1892. It is known from Mexico and Panama.BioLib.cz - Sympleurotis armatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1892
title: Sympleurotis armatus
